  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sea of Change</strong>  is my first game, developed solo on a very small budget (less than $300). It’s my best attempt yet, and while I wanted to add even more features, some things were beyond my current skill level. I had to put it out there or risk getting stuck in development forever. I truly appreciate any support. I’m already planning to expand on this with a sequel and create more games in the future!<br><strong><br>It </strong>is a game where you have to defend your base from enemies at night! Collect the resources on your island by destroying trees or enemies! Set sail to find islands that contain resources, and return to your base to build and defend! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Features:</u></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Constantly build, expand, and upgrade your base.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Acquire resources to build more and better defenses.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the seas to find other islands and collect resources! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each game is unique as all islands are procedurally generated.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DEFEND AGAINST ENEMIES:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891160/extras/054ffd6b08b046423ada4dc7a1af88ad.poster.avif?t=1744999472\" width=768 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891160/extras/054ffd6b08b046423ada4dc7a1af88ad.webm?t=1744999472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891160/extras/054ffd6b08b046423ada4dc7a1af88ad.mp4?t=1744999472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BUILD YOUR BASE:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891160/extras/f890ee96bcc3b90df07ce2d13f0451f4.poster.avif?t=1744999472\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891160/extras/f890ee96bcc3b90df07ce2d13f0451f4.webm?t=1744999472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891160/extras/f890ee96bcc3b90df07ce2d13f0451f4.mp4?t=1744999472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>EXPLORE THE SEAS:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891160/extras/9d77b078d18580835f0f0a0e4ab2e9b8.poster.avif?t=1744999472\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891160/extras/9d77b078d18580835f0f0a0e4ab2e9b8.webm?t=1744999472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891160/extras/9d77b078d18580835f0f0a0e4ab2e9b8.mp4?t=1744999472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>COLLECT RESOURCES:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891160/extras/543ccf655d82305bb7ffa4bb897c7057.poster.avif?t=1744999472\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891160/extras/543ccf655d82305bb7ffa4bb897c7057.webm?t=1744999472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891160/extras/543ccf655d82305bb7ffa4bb897c7057.mp4?t=1744999472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sea of Change</strong>  is my first game, developed solo on a very small budget (less than $300). It’s my best attempt yet, and while I wanted to add even more features, some things were beyond my current skill level. I had to put it out there or risk getting stuck in development forever. I truly appreciate any support. I’m already planning to expand on this with a sequel and create more games in the future!<br><strong><br>It </strong>is a game where you have to defend your base from enemies at night! Collect the resources on your island by destroying trees or enemies! Set sail to find islands that contain resources, and return to your base to build and defend! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Features:</u></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Constantly build, expand, and upgrade your base.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Acquire resources to build more and better defenses.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the seas to find other islands and collect resources! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each game is unique as all islands are procedurally generated.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DEFEND AGAINST ENEMIES:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891160/extras/054ffd6b08b046423ada4dc7a1af88ad.poster.avif?t=1744999472\" width=768 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891160/extras/054ffd6b08b046423ada4dc7a1af88ad.webm?t=1744999472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891160/extras/054ffd6b08b046423ada4dc7a1af88ad.mp4?t=1744999472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BUILD YOUR BASE:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891160/extras/f890ee96bcc3b90df07ce2d13f0451f4.poster.avif?t=1744999472\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891160/extras/f890ee96bcc3b90df07ce2d13f0451f4.webm?t=1744999472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891160/extras/f890ee96bcc3b90df07ce2d13f0451f4.mp4?t=1744999472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>EXPLORE THE SEAS:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891160/extras/9d77b078d18580835f0f0a0e4ab2e9b8.poster.avif?t=1744999472\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891160/extras/9d77b078d18580835f0f0a0e4ab2e9b8.webm?t=1744999472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891160/extras/9d77b078d18580835f0f0a0e4ab2e9b8.mp4?t=1744999472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>COLLECT RESOURCES:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891160/extras/543ccf655d82305bb7ffa4bb897c7057.poster.avif?t=1744999472\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891160/extras/543ccf655d82305bb7ffa4bb897c7057.webm?t=1744999472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/st